            <div class="title">
                Foreign Policy (President Truman&#39;s Declaration)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1945-11-07/debates/1ea31e32-b813-49dd-a84c-09d470c7ab88/MilitaryDetentionBarrack(Conditions)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
