                Mr. Logan  (Liverpool, Scotland)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-93643af5-823e-4610-a5cf-6adbff1d9351" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
