<p class="">I said that if the bomb went off there would be no working class.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-93643af5-823e-4610-a5cf-6adbff1d9351" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
